description: This Chinese restaurant run by owner Suili Zhou has a beautiful and elegant ambience in which the chef is keen to introduce guests to the authentic culinary traditions of his homeland via a selection of refined dishes. You’ll also find an interesting choice of teas – served in traditional style at your table – plus a selection of champagnes and Italian sparkling wines.
